{"tid":988222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【噁心慎入】頸邊粒瘡牛油果咁大 「唧瘡大師」清出稠膿：似糊仔","createTime":"2019-01-20T01:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T00:14:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":81,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"bf28a88d6772b156328010b87be81e3cd617a2ec","tid":988222,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:04:07.000Z","msg":"美國一位鋼管舞舞蹈員頸上長有巨瘡，大得像牛油果般，令她一生受盡欺凌及尷尬。她決定找上有「唧瘡大師」（Dr Pimple Popper）之稱的知名皮膚科醫生，為她除去纏擾她12年的巨瘡。<br />\n22歲的亞米萊特（Yamileth）10歲起就有這粒巨瘡，她表示：「這影響了我與他人交流，他們看着這粒瘡而不是我的臉，令我感到很尷尬。」<br />\n她表示曾因巨瘡而被欺凌，她說：「要隱藏這巨瘡是很折磨人，我只是想踏單車時不用再戴圍巾或把頭髮放到前面。我讀高中時就曾因巨瘡被欺凌，他們會挑剔我。」<br />\n亞米萊特找「唧瘡大師」、加州著名皮膚科醫生桑德拉（Sandra Lee）為她除去巨瘡，在局部麻醉後，甫割開巨瘡已噴出奶白色液體，後來稠膿混著血水流出，去到後來更呈忌廉狀，甚為噁心。<br />\n桑德拉也認為這是她處理過最噁心的瘡，「我從未見過像亞米萊特身上般的膿瘡，我覺得那（穢物）像糊仔。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190119/large/1547884752_e5d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190119%2Flarge%2F1547884752_e5d2.jpg&h=679d30ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59155853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59155853&d=ugoaPMJGAUOlqu0hTQrapIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4c3d66d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59155853&h=0fee435c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59155853</a>"},{"pid":"227dee022230f0415bb853bb9072a7eb62e74f1d","tid":988222,"uid":4574,"like":369,"dislike":2,"score":367,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"咁大粒毒瘤<br />\n都忍到12年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81b13d32922fc561bfc96ef3522161cb90df000","tid":988222,"uid":146435,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime